    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">The Aberdeen Board of Elections oversees the administration of all City of Aberdeen municipal elections, including voter registration, candidate qualification, polling place operations, and certification of results.</p>

    <div class="bg-gov-blue rounded-xl p-6 text-white">
